reviewText: This is a good method of helping you prepare you for the California Real Estate Sales or Broker's Exam. The 5-DVD set has more than "15.5 hours" of review. Since the year "2004" ALL DVDs and Matching Fill-In-The-Blank Workbooks have been scripted by Dwight Norris (the instructor) to be compatible. If you want to compare Real Estate Lecture Review Videos online, "ebay" & "ioffer" have similar products. I recommend that you go through as many Questions as possible to prepare for the California Exam.
